  "title": "DevOps & Application Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role: DevOps & Application Engineer</strong><br /><strong>Location: Singapore</strong><br /><br /><strong>We are partnering with a leading telecom client</strong> to hire a DevOps & Application Engineer to drive cloud-native delivery, CI/CD automation, and Kubernetes operations.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Design and manage CI/CD pipelines using Jen​kins (Pipeline-as-Code)</li><li>Administer Kubernetes clusters (EKS / OpenShift) and Helm charts</li><li>Implement GitOps workflows (ArgoCD / Flux)</li><li>Build and manage AWS infrastructure using Terraform / CloudFormation</li><li>Contribute application code in Python, Go, or TypeScript</li><li>Set up observability using Splunk, Prometheus, Grafana, CloudWatch<br /></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li>4+ years of experience in DevOps / SRE / Software Engineering</li><li>Strong hands-on experience with Kubernetes, Jenkins, and AWS</li><li>Experience with Infrastructure as Code and GitOps</li><li>Comfortable with Linux, networking, and scripting</li><li>CKA / CKAD / AWS certifications are a plus</li></ul><p><br /><em>UEN: 202329526G</em></p><p><em>EA Licence: 23S2061</em></p>",
